  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>After a nuclear war, there is an apocalypse around the world and you are one of the survivors.<br><br>By chance you stumble upon an abandoned town where no one has lived for a long time.<br><br>You will have to take fate into your own hands.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>Gameplay:</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy goods and sell them to customers.<br><br><strong>In the game you will find:<br>- </strong>Big city<strong><br>- </strong>Store employee simulator<strong><br>- </strong>Radio<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268640/extras/5f653ca46c4f0a7404f81a49ff999944.avif?t=1735313252\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268640/extras_big/5f653ca46c4f0a7404f81a49ff999944.avif?t=1735313252 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>After a nuclear war, there is an apocalypse around the world and you are one of the survivors.<br><br>By chance you stumble upon an abandoned town where no one has lived for a long time.<br><br>You will have to take fate into your own hands.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong>Gameplay:</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy goods and sell them to customers.<br><br><strong>In the game you will find:<br>- </strong>Big city<strong><br>- </strong>Store employee simulator<strong><br>- </strong>Radio<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268640/extras/5f653ca46c4f0a7404f81a49ff999944.avif?t=1735313252\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268640/extras_big/5f653ca46c4f0a7404f81a49ff999944.avif?t=1735313252 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
